name: NoDev AI
description: NODEV is an advanced no-code platform that seamlessly orchestrates the automatic generation of both front-end and back-end code within minutes, drastically reducing development time. Engineered for individuals without technical expertise, NODEV empowers users to construct sophisticated applications effortlessly, eliminating the need for manual coding. From intuitive UI design to comprehensive database management, it delivers an all-encompassing full-stack solution, equipped with an array of powerful tools and utilities that redefine the efficiency and accessibility of modern software development
